sourcesContent:
<ion-header [translucent]="true">
  <ion-toolbar>
    <ion-title>perfil-add</ion-title>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content [fullscreen]="true">
  <ion-header collapse="condense">
    <ion-toolbar>
      <ion-title size="large">perfil-add</ion-title>
    </ion-toolbar>
  </ion-header>

  <ion-item>
    <ion-label position="floating">Tipo</ion-label>
    <ion-input [(ngModel)]="tipo" name="tipo" type="text"></ion-input>
  </ion-item>

  <ion-item>
    <ion-label position="floating">Id_Usuario</ion-label>
    <ion-input [(ngModel)]="usuario" name="usuario" type="text"></ion-input>
  </ion-item>

  <ion-button (click)="addPerfil()" expand="full">Añadir Perfil</ion-button>
  <ion-button (click)="gotoPerfilList()" expand="full">Ver lista de perfiles</ion-button>
</ion-content>
